com.organization4242.delmgorb.view

Class MainWindowView

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.organization4242.delmgorb.view.AbstractView
      • com.organization4242.delmgorb.view.MainWindowView

  • public class MainWindowView
extends AbstractView
    Represents main window with all UI controls. It uses 5 panels to place UI controls ans then place all panel inside the main panel. Also it adds focus listener in order to select all text in text fields when it gains focus. All controls are empty in the resulting window, use MainWindowController to set all values.
    Author:
    Murzinov Ilya
